      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Stop Targeting Americans in Natural Disasters with Unconscionable Prices Act of 2017 or the STAND UP Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill makes it unlawful for any person to sell or offer for sale a consumer good or service in a major disaster area at a price that (1) is unconscionably excessive, and (2) indicates&nbsp;that the seller is taking unfair advantage of the circumstances related to&nbsp;the major disaster to increase prices unreasonably.</p>]]></text>
